- low level networking interface
- rodzaj inter-process-communication (IPC) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inter-process_communication
- The most common type of socket applications are client-server applications, where one side acts as the server and waits for connections from clients.
- są Internet sockets oraz UNIX domain sockets (komunikacja pomiędzy procesami tego samego hosta)

socket funkcje i metody:
    socket()
    bind()
    listen()
    accept()
    connect()
    connect_ex()
    send()
    recv()
    close()

- do komunikacji sockety używają TCP lub rzadziej UDP
- wiki socket: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Network_socket
- socket workflow https://files.realpython.com/media/sockets-tcp-flow.1da426797e37.jpg
- web browser’s “client” socket and the web server’s “client” socket are identical beasts
